{"tid":1399632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府管理層教你如何阻止8月5日全港大罷工","createTime":"2019-08-03T08:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:38:16.000Z","uid":34230,"like":95,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b10f9eabf5b0498d35360940ba079897b324f5e5","tid":1399632,"uid":34230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"收到通知，有政府部門要求公務員取消喺8月5日預先批准嘅休假，但有管理層好唔小心咁透露咗一樣野(亦係唯一一樣)會令情況有變，就係如果主要幹道同地鐵被人堵塞以致返唔工， 咁員工返唔到工或者遲到大半日都係合情，合理同可以體諒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以要叫人千祈唔好堵塞主要道路，唔係嘅話就連未過三年試用期嘅公務員都可以合情，合理哋返唔到工，或者遲到大半日！！！你哋知啦！公職服務有一日半日嘅影響都可以好麻煩㗎嘛！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請廣傳，好人一生平安。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83937e179df9be2d6c5fc25796ef9fadaf564c5","tid":1399632,"uid":37081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:34:23.000Z","msg":"好過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c4ef5d11f28d148cc1266cf67af6a9748b57b5","tid":1399632,"uid":289969,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"唔俾人病？"},{"pid":"94eca95fe3eeadf943814584bdc8a7ffd7bcba02","tid":1399632,"uid":130695,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:37:29.000Z","msg":"果日班三毛係咁屌5/8 不合作都知咩料啦<br />\n唔好話一日罷工<br />\n政府跟本好撚怕班AO 叛變"},{"pid":"0d1f2dc3529e9bafcb37b30cbee3e7be68d8f84f","tid":1399632,"uid":34230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:43:21.000Z","msg":"其實有邊幾條主要幹道同地鐵站一俾人堵塞就好大件事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5c8b25f1bf3afc31bed4f8db9272fe4a92df85","tid":1399632,